<H3> <TI>   Sonatrach: Plans To Modernize Discussed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sonatrach: Plans To Modernize Discussed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AF0146B Algiers EL WATAN in French 16 Mar 94 p 13 </F>
<F P=103> 94AF0146B </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers EL WATAN </F>
