<H3> <TI>   Figures on Births, Marriages, Work, Housing </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Figures on Births, Marriages, Work, Housing </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AF0134B Algiers ALGERIE ACTUALITE in French 7 Feb 94 pp 
11, 12 </F>

<F P=103> 94AF0134B </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ALGERIE ACTUALITE </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


